Package: lmmprobe
Type: Package
Title: Sparse High-Dimensional Linear Mixed Modeling with a Partitioned Empirical Bayes ECM Algorithm
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2026-02-18
Author: Anja Zgodic, Alex McLain, Peter Olejua
Maintainer: Anja Zgodic <azgodic@email.sc.edu>
Description: Implements a partitioned Empirical Bayes ECM algorithm for sparse high-dimensional linear mixed modeling. The package provides efficient estimation and inference for mixed models with high-dimensional fixed effects.
